longBusinessSummary: JB Foods Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the production and sale of cocoa ingredient products in Malaysia, Singapore, the United States, Indonesia, and internationally. It offers cocoa mass, cocoa butter, and cocoa powder under the JB Cocoa brand. The company also procures, markets, and sells cocoa beans and ingredients, and related products, as well as raw materials; and leases properties. It sells its products to trade houses and end users, such as food and beverage, and confectionery manufacturers. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Gelang Patah, Malaysia.
